snippet.title: Wario Ware: Smooth Moves - Wario (High Score Run)
snippet.description:
*Read description first*

Let me give it a shot for a high score.

Key Notes:
- Wario has the least microgames from the lot, though some can get frustrating as the speed goes up.
- Every four microgames, the speed increases. Every 8 microgames, you'll be faced by a boss.

Watch, enjoy, and comment, everyone.
